== ccfl electronic inverter ==

The CCFL (Cold Cathode Fluorescent Lamp) inverter works in general the same as other converter systems in a much smaler scale.

[[Image:CCFL inverter schema.PNG|thumb|right|CCFL inverter schema|300px]]

[[Image:to 220.PNG|thumb|right|to 220|300px]]




schema components:

Q1 , Q2 = NPN TIP31, to-220 

R1 , R2 = 8.2 KOhms

D1 , D2 = 1N4001 / 4148

C1 = 10uF , 25V , 

C2 = 22 pF , 2KV

L1 = 80uH

T1 = FE16C or equivalent transformer 






